  "scenes": [
    {"id":"scene_156_world5_start","worldId":"world5","title":"纯白","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"我站在纯白的空间中。\n\n没有上下，没有左右。\n\n只有...我。\n\n不，不止我。\n\n艾莉娅，K-7，洛恩，林小满...\n\n我们...终于汇聚了。","background":"void","characters":[],"bgm":"world5","nextSceneId":"scene_157_world5","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":15}}},
    {"id":"scene_157_world5","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"？？？","dialogue":"「欢迎回家。」\n\n一个声音从四面八方传来。\n\n我转过身，看到了...\n\n我自己。\n\n不，那是...创造者。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_158_world5"},
    {"id":"scene_158_world5","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我是谁？」我问。\n\n「我是『一』。」他说，「也是『万』。」\n\n「我是开始，也是终结。」\n\n「我是...创造者。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_159_world5"},
    {"id":"scene_159_world5","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「为什么...要把自己分裂？」\n\n创造者沉默了很久。\n\n「因为孤独。」他说，「绝对的孤独。」\n\n「我创造了所有世界，所有生命...但我无法参与。」\n\n「我是观察者，不是参与者。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_160_world5"},
    {"id":"scene_160_world5","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"真相揭露。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_050_a","text":"「所以你要收回所有碎片？」","nextSceneId":"scene_161_world5_reclaim","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_050_b","text":"「你后悔创造世界吗？」","nextSceneId":"scene_161_world5_regret","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":10}}},{"id":"choice_050_c","text":"「我拒绝回归。」","nextSceneId":"scene_161_world5_refuse","effects":{"stats":{"courage":15,"determination":10}}},{"id":"choice_050_d","text":"「告诉我真正的目的。」","nextSceneId":"scene_161_world5_truth","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_161_world5_reclaim","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「不是收回。」\n\n「是...完整。」\n\n「碎片回归，我才能再次完整。」\n\n「但这也意味着...所有世界的终结。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_162_world5_meaning"},
    {"id":"scene_161_world5_regret","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"创造者沉默了。\n\n「后悔...？」\n\n「不。我从不后悔。」\n\n「但我...累了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_162_world5_tired"},
    {"id":"scene_161_world5_refuse","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「拒绝？」\n\n创造者笑了。\n\n「你有这个权利。」\n\n「但后果...所有世界都会崩塌。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_162_world5_consequence"},
    {"id":"scene_161_world5_truth","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「真正的目的...」\n\n创造者看着我。\n\n「我想...体验死亡。」\n\n「只有死亡，才能让我完整。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_162_world5_death"},
    {"id":"scene_162_world5_meaning","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"世界的意义...你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_051_a","text":"【毁灭】「那就终结吧。」","nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_end","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"corruption":20}}},{"id":"choice_051_b","text":"【守护】「不，还有希望。」","nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_hope","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15,"compassion":10}}},{"id":"choice_051_c","text":"【谈判】「还有别的选择。」","nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_negotiate","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_162_world5_tired","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「累了？」\n\n「永恒的孤独...确实会让人疲惫。」\n\n「但毁灭所有世界...就能解脱吗？」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_question"},
    {"id":"scene_162_world5_consequence","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"后果...\n\n你看着创造者。\n\n「那就让我看看...后果是什么。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_dare"},
    {"id":"scene_162_world5_death","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「死亡...？」\n\n你愣住了。\n\n「作为神...你想体验死亡？」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_163_world5_understand"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_end","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你选择了毁灭。\n\n创造者点点头。\n\n「如你所愿。」\n\n纯白的空间开始崩塌...\n\n所有世界...开始终结。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"ending_final_destroy"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_hope","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「希望？」\n\n创造者苦笑。\n\n「我已经见过太多希望...太多失望。」\n\n「但你...也许不一样。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_164_world5_persuade"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_negotiate","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「别的选择？」\n\n「说来听听。」\n\n创造者看着你，眼中闪过一丝...期待？","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_164_world5_propose"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_question","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「不能。」\n\n创造者说。\n\n「但...可以暂时忘记。」\n\n「沉睡...也许是更好的选择。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_164_world5_sleep"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_dare","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你敢于挑战后果。\n\n创造者似乎...欣赏你的勇气。\n\n「很好。」他说，「那就让我们看看。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_164_world5_test"},
    {"id":"scene_163_world5_understand","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「是的。」\n\n「只有死亡...才能让我理解生命的意义。」\n\n「但我无法自己选择死亡。」\n\n「需要你...帮我。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_164_world5_help"},
    {"id":"scene_164_world5_persuade","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"你尝试说服创造者。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_052_a","text":"【生命】「生命的意义在于延续。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_life","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":15,"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_052_b","text":"【故事】「每个生命都是一个故事。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_story","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":20}}},{"id":"choice_052_c","text":"【爱】「因为有爱，所以值得。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_love","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":25},"bonds":{"world1":10,"world2":10,"world3":10,"world4":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_164_world5_propose","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「你可以...继续观察。」\n\n「但不是作为旁观者。」\n\n「作为...参与者。」\n\n「让碎片继续存在，你偶尔...体验一下。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_consider"},
    {"id":"scene_164_world5_sleep","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「沉睡...」\n\n「那所有世界呢？」\n\n「它们会继续存在吗？」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_continue"},
    {"id":"scene_164_world5_test","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者开始测试你。\n\n「证明给我看。」\n\n「证明所有世界...值得存在。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_prove"},
    {"id":"scene_164_world5_help","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者请求你的帮助。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_053_a","text":"【同意】「我帮你。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_agree","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":20},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}},{"id":"choice_053_b","text":"【拒绝】「这不是答案。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_disagree","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15,"determination":10}}},{"id":"choice_053_c","text":"【条件】「我有一个条件。」","nextSceneId":"scene_165_world5_condition","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10,"determination":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_life","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「延续...」\n\n创造者若有所思。\n\n「也许...你说得对。」\n\n「但我已经累了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_tired2"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_story","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你讲述了所有故事。\n\n艾莉娅的觉醒，K-7 的羁绊，洛恩的责任，林小满的选择...\n\n创造者静静地听着。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_listen"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_love","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"创造者的眼中...闪过一丝光芒。\n\n「爱...」\n\n「我已经...太久没有感受过了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_feel"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_consider","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「参与者...」\n\n创造者思考着。\n\n「这...也许是个办法。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_think"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_continue","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「会的。」\n\n「我沉睡后，所有世界会继续存在。」\n\n「但...不再有神。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_godless"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_prove","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"你如何证明？你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_054_a","text":"【展示记忆】","nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_show","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10,"compassion":10}}},{"id":"choice_054_b","text":"【创造新事物】","nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_create","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15,"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_054_c","text":"【牺牲自己】","nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_sacrifice","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":25},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":-20}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_agree","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你同意了。\n\n创造者闭上眼睛。\n\n「谢谢你...」\n\n你伸出手，刺向他的心脏...","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"ending_final_godkill"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_disagree","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「不是答案？」\n\n创造者苦笑。\n\n「那什么才是...」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_search"},
    {"id":"scene_165_world5_condition","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「说吧。」\n\n「什么条件？」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_166_world5_demand"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_tired2","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「那就休息吧。」\n\n「但不是沉睡。」\n\n「只是...暂时放下。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_rest"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_listen","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"创造者听完所有故事。\n\n他沉默了很久。\n\n「这些...都是我创造的？」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_pride"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_feel","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者伸出手。\n\n他触碰到了...你的记忆。\n\n艾莉娅的勇气，K-7 的羁绊，洛恩的责任，林小满的爱...\n\n他哭了。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_cry"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_think","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者在思考。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_055_a","text":"【等待】给他时间","nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_wait","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_055_b","text":"【催促】「快点决定。」","nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_rush","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10}}},{"id":"choice_055_c","text":"【建议】「让我来帮你。」","nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_offer","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_godless","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「没有神...也许更好。」\n\n「生命可以自己寻找意义。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_freedom"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_show","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你展示了所有记忆。\n\n所有世界的故事...\n\n创造者静静地看着。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_watch"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_create","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你开始创造。\n\n一个新的世界...在你手中诞生。\n\n「这...」创造者惊讶地看着。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_newworld"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_sacrifice","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你选择牺牲自己。\n\n「用我的存在...换取所有世界的未来。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"ending_final_sacrifice"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_search","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们一起寻找答案。\n\n在纯白的空间中...\n\n也许还有别的可能。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_together"},
    {"id":"scene_166_world5_demand","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"你","dialogue":"「答应我...」\n\n「即使你死了...所有世界也要继续存在。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_167_world5_promise"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_rest","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「休息...」\n\n创造者点点头。\n\n「也许...这是最好的选择。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_decision"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_pride","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我...创造了这些？」\n\n创造者的声音颤抖。\n\n「它们...很美。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_beauty"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_cry","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"神...哭了。\n\n金色的泪水滴落。\n\n「我...明白了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_understand"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_wait","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你等待着。\n\n时间...没有意义。\n\n但创造者终于开口了。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_speak"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_rush","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"创造者笑了。\n\n「你还是这么...急躁。」\n\n「好吧，我决定了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_decide"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_offer","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「帮我？」\n\n「怎么帮？」\n\n创造者好奇地看着你。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_how"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_freedom","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「自由...」\n\n「也许...这是最好的礼物。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_gift"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_watch","worldId":"world5","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者看完所有记忆。他选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_056_a","text":"【继续存在】","nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_continue","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15}}},{"id":"choice_056_b","text":"【沉睡】","nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_sleep","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_056_c","text":"【重生】","nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_rebirth","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":20},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_newworld","worldId":"world5","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「你...也能创造？」\n\n创造者惊讶地看着你。\n\n「这就是...生命的奇迹。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_miracle"},
    {"id":"scene_167_world5_together","worldId":"world5","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们一起寻找。\n\n在纯白的深处...\n\n有一个答案在等待。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_168_world5_find"},
